propertyFields.name: cacheTime
propertyFields.description: Time in UNIX epoch format when the event was stored by Alert Notification service

propertyFields.name: affectedActionId
propertyFields.description: Id of the action which was executed for the matched/undelivered event

propertyFields.name: deliveryStatus
propertyFields.description: Describes if the event has been delivered or not

propertyFields.name: failureReasons?
propertyFields.description: Describes why the delivery of an event failed, will only be returned if a query parameter is present
